Package com.rb.biz.marketdata.instrumentmaster

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    InstrumentMaster
    Answers two questions: for a Symbol / date combination, what is the (numeric) InstrumentId? What was the valid Symbol for an InstrumentId on a given date?
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    CascadingInstrumentMaster
    This acts as a plain InstrumentMaster, but it looks at 2 or more supplied InstrumentMasters in order, and returns the first non-empty value it finds.
    HardCodedAllowingEmptyInstrumentMaster
    Similar to HardCodedInstrumentMaster, except that it allows missing items and returns empty optionals from the InstrumentMaster interface methods, instead of throwing (as in getOrThrow).
    HardCodedInstrumentMaster
    A concrete implementation of the InstrumentMaster interface that
    InstrumentMasters
    Various utility methods for an InstrumentMaster
    NullInstrumentMaster
    A simple implementation of InstrumentMaster for cases when we want to say that we don't have an instrument master, but don't want to pass null because our codebase (as do most modern Java codebases) avoids nulls.
    OverridingToConstantDateInstrumentMaster
    A wrapper around an existing InstrumentMaster that overrides any date to be a fixed date.
